## ── Credentials ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Never commit real credentials. Copy .env.example → .env and fill in values.
.env

## ── .NET build artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
*.user
*.suo
.vs/
.vscode/

## ── Runtime state ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Incremental sync watermark written by JsonFileSyncStateStore
sync-state.json

## ── Logs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NLog rolling log files written to logs/ at runtime
logs/

## ── User secrets (development) ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Managed by `dotnet user-secrets`; stored outside the repo by design
secrets.json

## ── macOS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
